# SURGE conda environment (m3716)

The pre-built **surge** conda environment for this project is installed at:

`/global/common/software/m3716/asvillar/envs/surge` (Python 3.11)

**Activate by path** (e.g. when the env is not registered by name in conda):

`conda activate /global/common/software/m3716/asvillar/envs/surge`

**One-off command:**

`conda run -p /global/common/software/m3716/asvillar/envs/surge python ...`

See `envs/README.md` for details and for creating a local env from `environment.yml` instead.
